def: ^air-system
is: ^system
doc:
  A system for moving air to maintain indoor thermal comfort and/or air quality.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^conditioning
is: ^marker
doc:
  Related to cleaning, heating, cooling, humidifying, dehumidifying, ventilating or circulating  air. 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^air-conditioning-system
is: ^air-system
doc:
  A system for air treatment to control its temperature, humidity, cleanliness,
  and distribution to meet the requirements of a conditioned space. 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^conditioning
is: ^marker
doc:
  Related to cleaning, heating, cooling, humidifying, dehumidifying, ventilating
  or circulating  air.  
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^air-exhaust-system
is: ^air-system
doc:
  A system consisting of one or more fans that remove air from the building,
  causing outdoor air to enter by ventilation inlets or normal leakage paths
  through the building envelope.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^air-ventilation-system
is: ^air-system
doc:
  A system that supplies or removes air by natural or mechanical means to or
  from any space in order to provide outdoor air to the space. Such air may or
  may not have been conditioned. 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^elec-system
is: ^system
doc:
  A system that generates, converts, distributes, and/or stores electricity.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^evse-system
is: ^elec-system
doc:
  A system that supplies electricity to EVSE assembly equipment and its 
  auxiliary loads.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^lighting-system
is: ^elec-system
doc:
  A system designed to provide lighting.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^refrig-system
is: ^system
doc:
  Refrigerant distribution system for purposes of fulfilling 
  all or parts of a refrigeration cycle.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^water-system
is: ^system
doc:
  A system that supplies or collects potable or non-potable water in any state.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^chilled-water-system
is: ^water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates water in its liquid state below ambient temperature
  for the purpose of cooling a space or process.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^condenser-water-system
is: ^water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates water in its liquid state for the purpose of
  rejecting heat from a space or process.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^hot-water-system
is: ^water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates water in its liquid state for the purpose of heating
  a space or process.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^steam-system
is: ^water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates water in its vapor state for the purpose of heating
  a space or process.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^domestic-water-system
is: ^water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates potable water in its liquid state for purposes other
  than space conditioning and process requirements.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^domestic-cold-water-system
is: ^domestic-water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates potable cold water in its liquid state for purposes
  other than space cooling and process requirements.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^domestic-hot-water-system
is: ^domestic-water-system
doc:
  A system that circulates potable hot water in its liquid state for purposes
  other than space heating and process requirements.
